Package: gtm
Type: Package
Title: Generative Topographic Mapping
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(person("Scott", "Locklin", email = "scott_locklin@yahoo.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ondrej", "Such", role = "aut"),
    person("Markus", "Svensen", role = "ctb",
    comment = "Original MATLAB implementation"))
Description: Fits Generative Topographic Maps (GTM), a probabilistic
    alternative to Self-Organizing Maps (SOM) for nonlinear dimensionality
    reduction and visualization. Implements the EM algorithm from Bishop,
    Svensen, and Williams (1998) <doi:10.1162/089976698300017953> with
    rectangular and hexagonal latent grids, PCA initialization, and seven
    visualization types including density maps, U-matrix, component planes,
    and magnification factors.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: proxy, stats, graphics, grDevices
